    • Enum Constant Detail

      • DIJKSTRA

        public static final SubGraphFactory.ShortestPathAlgorithm DIJKSTRA
        Dijkstra algorithm implementation, wiki article. More general, works for graphs with loops, graphs with weighed edges, but really slow compared to BFS, approximately 10 times slower than BFS.

      • BREADTH_FIRST_SEARCH

        public static final SubGraphFactory.ShortestPathAlgorithm BREADTH_FIRST_SEARCH
        Path search with breadth first search - basic algorithm for graph traversing, wiki article. Works only for minimal spanning trees, i.e. graphs without loops, can't consider edges weights, but really fast (approximately 10 times faster than Dijkstra).
